Setswana ke puo e e buiwang mo mafatsheng a Aforika Borwa, Botswana, Namibia le Zimbabwe. Ke nngwe ya dipuo tsa semmuso kwa Aforika Borwa fa kwa Botswana gone e le puo e e tsewang e le yone ya lefatshe ka bophara (official language). Banni bangwe ba Botswana ba tsalwa ba sa bue Setswana jaaka Bakgalagadi, Bakalaka le ba bangwe. Ba se ithuta mo mebileng. 

Bontsi ba batho ba ba buang Setswana ba fitlhelwa kwa Aforika Borwa bogolo segolo mo diporofenseng tsa Bokone Bophirima (North West) le Kapa Bokone (Northern Cape). Batswana ba Aforika Borwa ba ka nna didikadike (million) di le 3.4 fa Batswana ba Botswana ba ka nna sedikadile le go feta (gongwe 1.3). Batswana ba Namibia le Ba Zimbabwe ba palo potlona. Legale ditirelo tsa kgaso tsa Namibia di gasa gape ka Setswana.

Setswana ke puo e e monatenate, e e nonneng ka e bile e buiwa mo mafatsheng a mane a a mo borwa jwa Aferika. Baithuti bangwe ba dipuo ba re Setswana ke nngwe ya dipuo tse di matswakabele thata go gaisa tse dingwe tsa borwa jwa Aferika. 

Setswana se na le manatesha puo a mantsi jaaka [[diane]],[[dithamalakane]] le [[maele]].
